# {{title}}

## Summary
{{"Respond ONLY with JSON per the system message. Use key prompt_1 for this value. Based solely on the provided context, write an information-dense summary in 120200 words: core problem/thesis, key arguments/steps, notable evidence/examples, main takeaway. No intro/conclusion phrases. Output Markdown only (no HTML tags), no code blocks, ASCII characters only. Do not include surrounding quotes."|replace:"/^'|'$/g":""|strip_tags:"p,div,span,code,pre"|replace:"/[^\x00-\x7F]/g":""}}

## Key points
{{"Respond ONLY with JSON per the system message. Use key prompt_2 for this value. Based solely on the provided context, return 35 bullet points as a Markdown list, each on its own line, prefixed exactly with '- ', 612 words, non-overlapping. No HTML, ASCII only, no trailing periods."|replace:"/^'|'$/g":""|strip_tags:"p,div,span,ul,ol,li"|replace:"/^\*\s/gm":"- "|replace:"/\s*\s*/g":"\n- "|replace:"/\s*-\s/g":"\n- "|replace:"/[^\x00-\x7F]/g":""}}
